Titolo: Math Blaster Mystery: The Great Brain Robbery

Anno: 1998

Descrizione: Math Blaster Mystery: The Great Brain Robbery, is a product in a line of educational products created by Davidson & Associates that takes place in a different universe from the original Math Blaster one. It has no relation to Davidson's earlier Apple II game "Math Blaster Mystery". The game was released in North America, Sweden and Spain. The game was remade in 1998 with the title "Math Blaster: Pre-Algebra". The game is regarded as a 'Review and Practice' type of software.